<B><U><FONT SIZE=+1>EverMon/EverGuild Website</FONT></U></B><BR>

<P>&nbsp&nbsp Welcome to the official homepage of EverMon and EverGuild
software.  The website has been re-designed in an attempt to make finding
the specific information that you are looking for, easier.  To the left of
the page, you will find a series of links for both EverMon and EverGuild,
which will tell you everything from a brief description of what each software
is, to the latest news, to how download the latest version, or get answers
to support questions.</P>

<B><U><FONT SIZE=+1>Hydra's UniNet Technology</FONT></U></B><BR>

<P>&nbsp&nbsp Both EverMon and EverGuild use Hydra Computer's UniNet Launcher
Software technology for the initial installation and for the version control
and update system.  by means of the Launcher application, we are able to roll
out and update versions of EverMon and EverGuild very quickly, without
requiring users to manually download updates from the internet.  The Launcher
application works almost the same as EverQuest's patch utility, except it
supports multiple applications, and allows you to download new applications
that you choose.</p>

<p>&nbsp&nbsp For more information on the Launcher application, downloading
and installing the launcher, or download and installing EverMon or EverGuild
from within the launcher, select the download link to the left for either
EverMon or EverGuild.</p>

